<% layout('layout') -%>
<h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Bulk import (XLSX)</h1>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
  Fayl format (sarlavhalar): 
  <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">
    test_id, question, correct_answer, answer_1, answer_2, answer_3, answer_4[, answer_5..answer_8]
  </code>
</p>

<div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 mb-5">
  <form method="post" action="/admin/questions/bulk" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="space-y-3">
    <div>
      <label class="text-sm text-gray-600">XLSX fayl</label>
      <input type="file" name="xlsx" accept=".xlsx" required class="mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border px-3 py-2" />
    </div>
    <button class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 text-white px-4 py-2">Yuklash</button>
  </form>
</div>

<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">
  * Eslatma: <br/>
  – <code>correct_answer</code> quyidagilardan biri bo‘lishi mumkin: <b>variant matni</b> (tavsiya etiladi), yoki <b>1..8</b>, yoki <b>A..H</b>. <br/>
  – Kamida 2 ta <code>answer_n</code> to‘ldirilgan bo‘lishi kerak.
</div>